    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category</strong>: Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Level 12+, Ningyo Clan</p><p>You have practiced spending your time to weave heart-moving stories into your songs, that even without knowing your tale before it ends, they have power.</p><ul><li>You gain an additional +2 Ballad die per long rest.</li></ul><p>At the start of a rest, roll a d8. You gain the following benfits based on the result. You may spend a Ballad die, to roll an additional time, and gain both effects (Reroll for Duplicate Effects)</p><ul><li>1-2: Your Ballad die granted to allies become a d12 until your next rest</li><li>3-4: When an Ally Spends a Ballad die, They gain temporary chakra equal to the result</li><li>5-6: Your Ballad Die may be spent to be added to damage rolls of a Jutsu Up to 3 times per casting</li><li>7: Your Ballad die reroll 1's, once each (excpet for this feature)</li><li>8: You may add your Charisma Modifier to any roll of a Ballad die (excpet for this feature)</li></ul>",
